8 Ball Pool





8 Ball Pool Game is a fun game to me since I love playing pool game in real life. If you are new into pool, this game will make it easier for you to play since the game instructions and rules are straightforward. Unlike other pool games, 8 Pool Game is unique in that you not only get to customize both your table and cue, but also get to purchase different cues with either the in-game chips or money from your pocket. What is more, fun is that you have the option of either playing the game with your Facebook friends or against an expert who is uniquely selected to match your pool skills.
